<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_View does not allow to pass it more than one helper path and helper prefix when instantiated with</p>

<p>new Zend_View(array('helperPath' = '/path/to/helper/dir'))</p>

<p>Perhaps the class could check whether the key is an array and perform an iteration over the elements in that array to fix this</p>

